OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,FStormont's Education Minister has
OL,7,Fannounced major reforms to GCSEs and A-
OL,8,Flevels which he said would put an end
OL,9,Fto an "inhumane, ineffective
OL,10,Fqualification system".
OL,12,FPaul Givan told MLAs his reforms would
OL,13,Fcurtail "high level of testing, high
OL,14,Flevel of anxiety for our young people
OL,15,F(and) high level of workload for
OL,16,Fteachers".
OL,26,@qD@GOUrD@UO]uD@IOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,FAS-levels will be scrapped and
OL,7,Freplaced with a new modular A-level
OL,8,Fwith three units of assessment taken
OL,9,Fover two years, with the aim of
OL,10,Fcutting the total number of exams.
OL,12,FControlled assessment and coursework
OL,13,Fwill be reduced in most subjects,
OL,14,Fexcept where it is "essential to
OL,15,Fassess practical skills".
OL,17,FMr Givan said the education system had
OL,18,Fbecome dominated by "teaching to the
OL,19,Ftest, leading to stress, anxiety, and
OL,20,Flost opportunities for genuine depth
OL,21,Fin learning".
OL,26,@vD@TOUwD@XO]zD@UOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,F"These reforms reduce unnecessary
OL,7,Fexams, give back precious teaching
OL,8,Ftime, and focus on what truly matters
OL,9,Ffor future success," he said.
OL,11,F"Northern Ireland pupils currently
OL,12,Ftake far more exams than their peers
OL,13,Fin England to achieve the same
OL,14,Fqualifications due to the AS
OL,15,Fstructure."
OL,17,FHe added: "Reducing controlled
OL,18,Fassessment and coursework will also
OL,19,Fhelp address workload burdens, equity
OL,20,Fissues, and the impact of AI on take-
OL,21,Fhome tasks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]sD@AOUwD@KO]yD@KOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,FIn the Stormont assembly on Tuesday
OL,7,FUUP leader Jon Burrows expressed
OL,8,Fconcern that removing coursework would
OL,9,F"increase the stress in young people
OL,10,Fand the stakes".
OL,12,FMr Givan said of those who responded
OL,13,Fto the public consultation, teachers
OL,14,Fwere "very much in favour of reducing
OL,15,Fthe controlled assessment aspect and
OL,16,Fcoursework, parents less so than
OL,17,Fpupils".
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,FHe added: "I think we need to ask
OL,7,Fourselves, for those who struggle
OL,8,Feducationally, for those who come from
OL,9,Fa more socially disadvantaged
OL,10,Fbackground, the time they have in
OL,11,Ffront of the teacher is the most
OL,12,Fcritical time that they can spend.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,F"They're not going to get additional
OL,7,Ftuition outside, they're not going to
OL,8,Fbe able to have that from a socially
OL,9,Fdisadvantaged background, not going to
OL,10,Fget maybe that additional support to
OL,11,Fcomplete coursework that is available
OL,12,Ffrom some families and they can be
OL,13,Fprovided by other people who may
OL,14,Fsupport that child.
OL,16,F"And so in terms of equity and
OL,17,Ffairness, what I'm proposing will
OL,18,Fcreate greater levels of equity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,F"It will have much higher levels of
OL,7,Fintegrity when it comes to making sure
OL,8,Fthat the work that is completed is
OL,9,Fauthentic in terms of it properly
OL,10,Fmeasures the pupil's performance and
OL,11,Fso this is a balanced approach that I
OL,12,Fhave taken."
OL,14,FThe minister added: "If we continue to
OL,15,Ftake the current approach, that means
OL,16,Fhigh level of testing, high level of
OL,17,Fanxiety for our young people, high
OL,18,Flevel of workload for teachers because
OL,19,Fof the excessive amount of content and
OL,20,Fthe excessive amount of controlled
OL,21,Fassessment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,F"That would be just repeating the doom
OL,7,Fthat we currently have and that the
OL,8,Fprofession are rightly complaining
OL,9,Fabout, and that pupils are feeling
OL,10,Fdoes not best serve their interests."
OL,12,FSinn Fein MLA Danny Baker said Mr
OL,13,FGivan "isn't listening to young people
OL,14,Fat all" and asked if he had consulted
OL,15,Fwith universities in the Republic of
OL,16,FIreland on his decision to scrap AS-
OL,17,Flevels.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,FMr Givan replied: "I am listening to
OL,7,Fyoung people, and if members in this
OL,8,FHouse have not listened to the extreme
OL,9,Flevels of anxiety that they have,
OL,10,Fbased upon the current system, the
OL,11,Fstatus quo, what people are saying is,
OL,12,F'if you don't want this change, then
OL,13,Fyou want to retain the status quo'.
OL,15,F"The status quo is a testing factory
OL,16,Fof our young people of repeated
OL,17,Fexaminations, for four years we put
OL,18,Fyoung people through repeated
OL,19,Fexaminations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,F"And when I give the evidence, and the
OL,7,Fevidence is that for AS-levels, when
OL,8,Fit comes to resits, only 7% of those
OL,9,Fwho resit actually improve the A-level
OL,10,Fgrade at the end of the process again,
OL,11,Fdo the math, that's 93% of people who
OL,12,Fresit AS-levels make no benefit to the
OL,13,FA-level outcome.
OL,15,F"Why would we put our young people
OL,16,Fthrough that kind of process?"
OL,18,FThe Education Minister further called
OL,19,Ffor Irish universities to "remove
OL,20,Ftheir partitionist agenda".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,FHe said: "Why is it that universities
OL,7,Fand the Republic of Ireland are
OL,8,Fincapable of accepting what Oxbridge
OL,9,Funiversities, what the Russell Group
OL,10,Funiversities, universities across the
OL,11,Fentire United Kingdom and here in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland accept for their top
OL,13,Fgraduates?
OL,15,F"So when it comes to this particular
OL,16,Fissue, we shouldn't comply with the
OL,17,Fdiscriminatory policy towards Northern
OL,18,FIreland students, which is
OL,19,Finstitutionalised by the Republic of
OL,20,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772640680
OL,3,CReforms for 'inhumane, ineffective' NI
OL,4,Cexam system
OL,6,F"We should take on the discrimination
OL,7,Fin the south, we should abolish the
OL,8,Fpartitionist agenda and I will work
OL,9,Fwith Sinn Fein to get rid of the
OL,10,Fdiscriminatory practices, which I do
OL,11,Fagree is prejudicial to our young
OL,12,Fpeople in Northern Ireland, but that
OL,13,Fis not a justification for retaining
OL,14,Fan inhumane, ineffective qualification
OL,15,Fsystem in Northern Ireland."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
